#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.62"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.62:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.62:0.2"
msgid "6. Avijjāvagga"
msgstr "6. Ignorance"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 62. Dutiyasabbupādānapariyādānasutta → pariyādinnaṃ 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.62:0.3"
msgid "62. Dutiyasabbupādānapariyādānasutta"
msgstr "62. The Depletion of All Fuel (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:1.1"
msgid "“Sabbupādānapariyādānāya vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you the principle for depleting all fuel."

msgctxt "sn35.62:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:1.3"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sabbupādānapariyādānāya dhammo?"
msgstr "And what is the principle for depleting all fuel?"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:2.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn35.62:2.2"
msgid "cakkhu niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "Is the eye permanent or impermanent?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:3.1"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:4.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:5.1"
msgid "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Suffering, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:6.1"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, kallaṃ nu taṃ samanupassituṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“But if it’s impermanent, suffering, and liable to fall apart, is it fit to "
"be regarded thus:"

msgctxt "sn35.62:6.2"
msgid "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’”ti?"
msgstr "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:7.1"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“No, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:8.1"
msgid "“Rūpā … pe …"
msgstr "“Sights …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:8.2"
msgid "cakkhuviññāṇaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "eye consciousness …"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.62:8.3"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante” … pe …."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:10.1"
msgid "“Cakkhusamphasso nicco vā anicco vā”ti?"
msgstr "eye contact …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:11.1"
msgid "“Anicco, bhante” … pe …."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:12.1"
msgid ""
"“Yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by eye "
"contact: is that permanent or impermanent?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:13.1"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante” … pe …."
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:14.1"
msgid "“Sotaṃ …"
msgstr "“Ear …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:14.2"
msgid "ghānaṃ …"
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:14.3"
msgid "jivhā …"
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:14.4"
msgid "kāyo …"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:14.5"
msgid "mano …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:14.6"
msgid "dhammā …"
msgstr "thoughts …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:14.7"
msgid "manoviññāṇaṃ …"
msgstr "mind consciousness …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:14.8"
msgid "manosamphasso …"
msgstr "mind contact …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:14.9"
msgid ""
"yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā, tampi niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"The pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind "
"contact: is that permanent or impermanent?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:15.1"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:16.1"
msgid "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:17.1"
msgid "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Suffering, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:18.1"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, kallaṃ nu taṃ samanupassituṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“But if it’s impermanent, suffering, and liable to fall apart, is it fit to "
"be regarded thus:"

msgctxt "sn35.62:18.2"
msgid "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’”ti?"
msgstr "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:19.1"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“No, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.35"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:20.1"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmimpi nibbindati, "
"rūpesupi nibbindati, cakkhuviññāṇepi nibbindati, cakkhusamphassepi "
"nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with the eye, "
"sights, eye consciousness, and eye contact."

msgctxt "sn35.62:20.2"
msgid ""
"Yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tasmimpi nibbindati … pe …"
msgstr ""
"And they grow disillusioned with the painful, pleasant, or neutral feeling "
"that arises conditioned by eye contact."

msgctxt "sn35.62:20.3"
msgid ""
"jivhāyapi nibbindati, rasesupi nibbindati, jivhāviññāṇepi nibbindati, "
"jivhāsamphassepi nibbindati, yampidaṃ jivhāsamphassapaccayā uppajjati … pe …"
msgstr "They grow disillusioned with the ear … nose … tongue … body …"

msgctxt "sn35.62:20.4"
msgid ""
"manasmimpi nibbindati, dhammesupi nibbindati, manoviññāṇepi nibbindati, "
"manosamphassepi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"They grow disillusioned with the mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, and "
"mind contact."

msgctxt "sn35.62:20.5"
msgid ""
"Yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"And they grow disillusioned with the painful, pleasant, or neutral feeling "
"that arises conditioned by mind contact."

msgctxt "sn35.62:20.6"
msgid ""
"Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati; vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "sn35.62:20.7"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’"

msgctxt "sn35.62:20.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sabbupādānapariyādānāya dhammo”ti."
msgstr "This is the principle for depleting all fuel.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.62:20.9"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.62:20.10"
msgid "Avijjāvaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.62:21.1"
msgid "Avijjā saṃyojanā dve,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.62:21.2"
msgid "āsavena duve vuttā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.62:21.3"
msgid "Anusayā apare dve,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.62:21.4"
msgid "pariññā dve pariyādinnaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.62:21.5"
msgid "Vaggo tena pavuccatīti."
msgstr ""
